aa(lp268
VAnd then what happened?
p269
aVAfter all this time, everybody joined in.
p270
aVAccording to the U.N.,
p271
aVnew cases of HIV
p272
aVdeclined by 90 percent,
p273
aVand according to the World Bank,
p274
aV7.7 million lives were saved.
p275
aVOtherwise there wouldn't be many Thais walking around today.
p276
aVSo it just showed you, you could do something about it.
p277
aV90 percent of the funding came from Thailand.
p278
aVThere was political commitment, some financial commitment,
p279
aVand everybody joined in the fight.
p280
aVSo just don't leave it to the specialists and doctors and nurses.
p281
aVWe all need to help.
